@startuml
title 最小描画から WebgApp への流れ

top to bottom direction
'left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName Yu Gothic UI
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 24
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #f7fbff
  FontColor black
}
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ranksep 20
skinparam nodesep 20

rectangle "1. Screen を作って await ready" as Low1
rectangle "2. Shader / projection を初期化" as Low2
rectangle "3. Space / eye / Shape を作る" as Low3
rectangle "4. clear -> draw -> present を回す" as Low4

rectangle "1. new WebgApp(options)" as App1
rectangle "2. await app.init()" as App2
rectangle "3. shape / model / scene を追加" as App3
rectangle "4. app.start() で入力 / HUD / 診断も回す" as App4

Low1 -down-> Low2
Low2 -down-> Low3
Low3 -down-> Low4
App1 -down-> App2
App2 -down-> App3
App3 -down-> App4

Low2 .right.> App2 : 描画の骨格を理解\nしたあとで標準構成へ

note top of Low1
ローレベルの最小構成
end note

note top of App1
WebgApp の標準構成
end note
@enduml
